%% Rollback process. See 12-rollback-plan.md
flowchart TB
  Trigger[need to roll back] --> Which{what stage}
  Which -- reads/writes enabled --> Flag[TENANCY_ENABLED=false -> revert to legacy keys, data intact]
  Which -- copy made --> Manifest[rollback-plan -> manifest of scoped targets]
  Manifest --> DelTargets[delete ONLY scoped targets under separate approved change]
  DelTargets --> LegacyIntact[legacy keys untouched throughout]
  Flag --> LegacyIntact
  LegacyIntact --> Safe[source of truth = legacy, no data loss]
